(** * Multisorted DTM typeclass *)
(**************************************************************)
Section MultisortedDTM_typeclasses.

  Context
    `{ix : Index}.

  (** ** Operations *)
  (**************************************************************)
  Section operations.

    Context
      (W : Type)
      (T : K -> Type -> Type)
      (U : Type -> Type).

    Class MReturn :=
      mret : forall (A : Type) (k : K), A -> T k A.

    Class MBind :=
      mbinddt : forall (F : Type -> Type) `{Map F} `{Pure F} `{Mult F} {A B : Type},
        (forall (k : K), W * A -> F (T k B)) -> U A -> F (U B).

  End operations.

  (** ** Definition of Kleisli composition *)
  (******************************************************************************)
  Definition compose_dtm
             {W : Type}
             {T : K -> Type -> Type}
             `{mn_op : Monoid_op W}
             `{mn_unit : Monoid_unit W}
             `{Map F} `{Mult F} `{Pure F}
             `{Map G} `{Mult G} `{Pure G}
             `{forall k, MBind W T (T k)}
             {A B C : Type}
             (g : forall k, W * B -> G (T k C))
             (f : forall k, W * A -> F (T k B)) : forall k, W * A -> F (G (T k C)) :=
    fun (k : K) '(w, a) => map (F := F) (mbinddt W T (T k) G (g ‚óª allK (incr w))) (f k (w, a)).

  Infix "‚ãÜdtm" := compose_dtm (at level 40) : tealeaves_scope.

  Section compose_dtm_lemmas.

      (W : Type)

      `{! MBind W T U}
      `{! forall k, MBind W T (T k)}
      {mn_op : Monoid_op W}
      {mn_unit : Monoid_unit W}.

    Context
      `{Applicative G}
      `{Applicative F}
      `{! Monoid W}
      {A B C : Type}
      (g : forall k, W * B -> G (T k C))
      (f : forall k, W * A -> F (T k B)).

  (** ** Decorated traversable premodule typeclass *)
  (******************************************************************************)
  Section PreModule.

    Context
      (W : Type)
      (T : K -> Type -> Type)
      (U : Type -> Type)
      `{! MReturn T}
      `{! MBind W T U}
      `{! forall k, MBind W T (T k)}
      {mn_op : Monoid_op W}
      {mn_unit : Monoid_unit W}.

    Class MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule :=
      { dtp_monoid :> Monoid W;
        dtp_mbinddt_mret : forall A,
            mbinddt W T U (fun a => a) (mret T A ‚óª allK extract) = @id (U A);
        dtp_mbinddt_mbinddt : forall
            (F : Type -> Type)
            (G : Type -> Type)
            `{Applicative F}
            `{Applicative G}
            `(g : forall k, W * B -> G (T k C))
            `(f : forall k, W * A -> F (T k B)),
            map (F := F) (mbinddt W T U G g) ‚àò mbinddt W T U F f =
            mbinddt W T U (F ‚àò G) (g ‚ãÜdtm f);
        dtp_mbinddt_morphism : forall
            (F : Type -> Type)
            (G : Type -> Type)
            `{ApplicativeMorphism F G œï}
            `(f : forall k, W * A -> F (T k B)),
            œï (U B) ‚àò mbinddt W T U F f =
            mbinddt W T U G ((fun k => œï (T k B)) ‚óª f);
      }.

  End PreModule.

  (** ** Decorated traversable monad *)
  (******************************************************************************)
  Section DTM.

    Context
      (W : Type)
      (T : K -> Type -> Type)
      `{! MReturn T}
      `{! forall k, MBind W T (T k)}
      {mn_op : Monoid_op W}
      {mn_unit : Monoid_unit W}.

    Class MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad :=
      { dtm_pre :> forall k, MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T (T k);
        dtm_mbinddt_comp_mret :
        forall k F `{Applicative F}
          `(f : forall k, W * A -> F (T k B)),
          mbinddt W T (T k) F f ‚àò mret T A k = f k ‚àò pair ∆µ;
      }.

  End DTM.

End MultisortedDTM_typeclasses.

Arguments mret {ix} _%function_scope {MReturn} {A}%type_scope _ _.
Arguments mbinddt {ix} {W}%type_scope {T} (U)%function_scope {MBind} F%function_scope {H H0 H1} {A B}.

#[local] Infix "‚ãÜdtm" := compose_dtm (at level 40) : tealeaves_scope.

(** ** Derived operations on DTMs *)
(******************************************************************************)
Section derived_operations.

  Context
    (U : Type -> Type)
    `{MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T U}.

  (** *** Definitions *)
  (******************************************************************************)
  Section definitions.

    Definition mapMret `{Map F} {A:Type}:
      forall (k: K), F A -> F (T k A) :=
      vec_apply (fun k => map (A := A) (B := T k A)) (mret T).

    Context
      {A B : Type}
      (F : Type -> Type)
      `{Map F} `{Mult F} `{Pure F}.

    Definition mbindd (f : forall k, W * A -> T k B) : U A -> U B :=
      mbinddt U (fun x => x) f.

    Definition mmapdt (f : forall k, W * A -> F B) : U A -> F (U B) :=
      mbinddt U F (mapMret ‚óª f).

    Definition mbindt (f : forall k, A -> F (T k B)) : U A -> F (U B) :=
      mbinddt U F (f ‚óª allK extract).

    Definition mbind (f : forall k, A -> T k B) : U A -> U B :=
      mbindd (f ‚óª allK extract).

    Definition mmapd (f : forall k, W * A -> B) : U A -> U B :=
      mbindd (mret T ‚óª f).

    Definition mmapt (f : forall k, A -> F B) : U A -> F (U B) :=
      mmapdt (f ‚óª allK extract).

    Definition mmap (f : forall k, A -> B) : U A -> U B :=
      mmapd (f ‚óª allK extract).

  End definitions.

  Section special_cases.

    Context
      {A B : Type}
      (F : Type -> Type)
      `{Map F} `{Mult F} `{Pure F}.

(** ** Composition between <<mbinddt>> and special cases operations *)
(** Fusion laws for compositions of the form <<mbinddt ‚àò xxx>> or <<xxx ‚àò mbinddt>> *)
(******************************************************************************)
Section derived_operations_composition.

  Context
    (U : Type -> Type)
    `{MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T U}
    `{! MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad W T}
    `{Applicative F}
    `{Applicative G}
    {A B C : Type}.

  (** *** <<mbinddt>> on the right *)
  (******************************************************************************)
  
U: Type -> Type
ix: Index
W: Type

  W T
A: Type
F: Type -> Type
H1: Map F
H2: Pure F
H3: Mult F
H4: Applicative F
pure ‚àò id = pure

    reflexivity.
  Qed.

End DTM_laws.

(** * Derived structures on DTMs *)
(******************************************************************************)

(** ** Some mixed structure composition laws *)
(** Composition laws involving one of <<mbindd>>/<<mmapdt>>/<<mbindt>>
    and another operation that is not a special cases. *)
(******************************************************************************)
Section mixed_composition_laws.

  Context
    (U : Type -> Type)
    (F G : Type -> Type)
    `{Applicative F}
    `{Applicative G}
    `{MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T U}
    `{! MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad W T} {A B C : Type}.

  (** *** <<mbindd>> *)
  (** Operations with traversals are not special cases of <<mbindd>>. *)

  (fun (k : K) '(w, a) =>
   map (g k ‚óã pair w) (f k (w, a)))

  (** *** <<mmapdt>> *)
  (** Operations with joins are not special cases of <<mmapdt>>. *)
  (******************************************************************************)
  
U, F, G: Type -> Type
H: Map F

H1: Mult F
H2: Applicative F

H4: Pure G
H5: Mult G
H6: Applicative G

H8: MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T U
MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad0: MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad
  W T
A, B, C: Type
forall (g : K -> W * B -> G C) (f : W * A ~k~> T B),
mmapdt U G g ‚àò mbindd U f =
mbinddt U G
  (fun (k : K) '(w, a) =>
   mmapdt (T k) G (g ‚óª allK (incr w)) (f k (w, a)))

(** ** Decorated monads (<<mbindd>>) *)
(******************************************************************************)
Definition compose_dm
           `{ix : Index}
           {W : Type}
           {T : K -> Type -> Type}
           `{mn_op : Monoid_op W}
           `{mn_unit : Monoid_unit W}
           `{forall k, MBind W T (T k)}
           {A B C : Type}
           (g : forall k, W * B -> T k C)
           (f : forall k, W * A -> T k B) : forall k, W * A -> T k C :=
  fun k '(w, a) => mbindd (T k) (g ‚óª allK (incr w)) (f k (w, a)).

Infix "‚ãÜdm" := compose_dm (at level 40).

H0: MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T U
MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad0: MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad
  W T
A, B, C: Type
g: B ~k~> T C
f: W * A ~k~> T B
k: K
w: W
a: A
mbindd (T k) ((g ‚óª allK extract) ‚óª allK (incr w))
  (f k (w, a)) =
mbindd (T k) (g ‚óª allK extract) (f k (w, a))
 
U: Type -> Type
ix: Index
W: Type
T: K -> Type -> Type
MReturn0: MReturn T
MBind0: MBind W T U
H: forall k : K, MBind W T (T k)
mn_op: Monoid_op W
mn_unit: Monoid_unit W
H0: MultiDecoratedTraversablePreModule W T U
MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad0: MultiDecoratedTraversableMonad
  W T
A, B, C: Type
g: B ~k~> T C
f: W * A ~k~> T B
k: K
w: W
a: A
(g ‚óª allK extract) ‚óª allK (incr w) = g ‚óª allK extract

    now ext j [w2 b].
  Qed.

End DecoratedMonad.
